transcript.text: We are very excited to invite you to meet us at On Print Shop.
Since 2006, we are working with print companies to offer modern customer experience in automate order management to grow shares.
Why you should talk to us, Listen to our customers.
If you are in a short run business, then the biggest challenge is generating more and more short run jobs because the run lines are small and the machine's speed is fast.
So you need to turn around a larger number of jobs in a day being in online prisons.
So a lot of client who wanted to reach out to us, they could use this online platform and actually get all their print requirement done online.
So definitely it helped us and we added a lot of new clients also during this.
Now we can do business all over the world, not only Gujarat and we are not limited to India only.
If you want to grow the business, it should be online.

It is not important, but it is mandatory right now because the customer reach you're getting through online and it's very easy for customer also because they are getting a wide option, they are getting what they want to choose.
